      • asList

        public java.util.List<DbxRecord> asList()
        Returns a list containing all the resulting records, loaded into memory. The resulting list can be freely modified (e.g. sorted), and doing so will affect the view of the data through this query object (e.g. through DbxTable.QueryResult.iterator(). Modifying the list won't cause records to be inserted or deleted in the datastore.
